Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.common

Common interfaces, base classes and some exceptions.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
BaseObject The base interface for all meta and data objects.
DataObject An interface for simple DataObjects.
MetaBuilder An interface for building meta based XML from in memory objects.
MetaLookup Interface that provides quick access for looking up metadata.
MetaObject Base interface for all meta objects (CVS meta, HL7 V3 meta, etc).
MetaParser An interface for parsing meta based XML into memory objects.
 

Class Summary
BaseObjectImpl The default implementation for the base class for all meta and data objects.
BaseResult A base class that contains validation resuts (errors, warning, etc.) after a particular action takes place.
DataObjectImpl A simple implementation of the DataObject interface.
MetaBuilderBase Base class to build a meta XML file
MetaObjectImpl Base class for all meta objects (CVS meta, HL7 V3 meta, etc).
VocabConstants Contains constants for all the HL7 vocabulary domains.
 

Exception Summary
ApplicationException An application exception is a custom exception thrown by the application or a third-party library.
DataException An application exception that is specific to data related functionality.
FunctionException An application exception that is specific to the function subsystem.
MetaException An application exception that is specific to meta related functionality.
SystemException A system exception is defined as either a checked exception or an unchecked exception.
ValidationException An application exception that that occurs when business rules are violated.
VocabularyException A validation exception that is specific to vocabulary validation.
